
The new Tpda

The goal is to make a database application framework that is easy to
maintain and develop and easy to use in the process of creating new
applications.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Tpda


